I"•<p>This is a community curated list of different ways to use Home Assistant. Most of these examples are using the <a href="/getting-started/automation/">automation</a> integration and other built-in <a href="/integrations/#automation">automation related</a> and <a href="/integrations/#organization">organization</a> integrations available.</p>
<p>For <a href="/integrations/python_script/"><code>python_script:</code> examples</a> visit the <a href="https://community.home-assistant.io/c/projects/scripts">Scripts section</a> in our forum.</p>
<p>New recipes can be added via the <a href="https://github.com/home-assistant/home-assistant.io/tree/current/source/_cookbook">home-assistant.io repository</a>.</p>
<div class='note'>
<p>A great place to find popular configurations is on this <a href="https://github.com/search?q=topic%3Ahome-assistant-config&amp;type=Repositories">GitHub search</a> for repositories with the <code>home-assistant-config</code> topic.</p>
</div>
